Title: Tous H2O EDT  -  50 ml(For Women)
Description: Refreshing like a drop of water in a dry, arid desert, H2O from the Italian fashion house of Tous, is more than simply a fragrance. Through an inspired concoction of citrusy and floral notes, H2O seeks to envelop you in a mist of sparkling clean freshness that rejuvenates you with its invigorating enticement. Through this luxury Eau de Toilette, renowned perfumer Sophia Constant seeks to establish an essential link between beauty and substance, and not just create another vapid and frivolous aroma. This feminine aquatic concentrate for women opens with a crisp fruity top note of organic lemon and honeyed lavender, which trails into an airy, delicately floral heart of rose and jasmine. The earthy, woody base note of cedar, white amber and scented Australian sandalwood adds a touch of pleasing warmth. H2O induces a sense of carefree living, of freedom from the chores of life, with its natural engaging aquatic aroma and its enticing warmth. Encased in a transparent briolette-cut blue vial fashioned with faceted crystals and a pyramid-like lid with a golden tag, H2O by Tous is like a pure drop of water - the source of all life. In keeping with this message, Tous also makes a social commitment - one percent of the retail price is donated to Oxfam, who provides clean drinking water to underdeveloped countries. H2O is pure sophistication that also sends a message.

Title: The Body Care Brazilian Wax White Chocolate(450 g)
Description: The Body Care white chocolate brazilian wax is specifically known for its properties, including energizing and revitalizing your skin. it has a proper consistency that is easy to spread evenly over a wider surface area of the skin. white chocolate Brazilian wax enriched with real white chocolate removes the hair from the root for a long period of time and helps in soothing the skin. Suitable on sensitive areas. Use the body care pre waxing gel to cleanse the area to be waxed.Direction of use : 1) Break one or two cubes as per your requirement. 2) put the cube in heater and turn on to maximum setting for a quick melt. 3) Turn heater down to normal temperature (50-60 degrees Celsius). 4) Clean the area to be waxed with The Body Care Pre-Wax Gel. 5) Apply wax in a thin layer in the direction of hair growth. Note: The quantity of The Body Care brazilian Wax is about 1/2 as thick as a typical hard wax and about twice as thick as The Body Care Liposoluble Wax. 6) Wait 1-2 seconds for the wax to cool and press firmly to ensure proper adhesion. 7) Hold the skin taut and remove the wax in one quick motion in the opposite direction of hair growth, parallel to the skin.
